{"id":12263,"date":"2020-09-04T13:28:17","date_gmt":"2020-09-04T13:28:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?page_id=12263"},"modified":"2021-05-18T12:12:33","modified_gmt":"2021-05-18T12:12:33","slug":"stades-delaboration-des-normes-gabonaises","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/normalisation\/comite-technique-de-la-normalisation\/stades-delaboration-des-normes-gabonaises\/","title":{"rendered":"Stades d\u2019\u00e9laboration des Normes Gabonaises"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-15a2fc99dc6b381cff9ecf51ac969b17\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-e16fb318b458089990881de8526097fa\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-f3cced51d1f993e65b49ec93a49f86b9\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-51362e10e9ed75c357940d39189b1478\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>STADES D&rsquo;\u00c9LABORATION DES NORMES GABONAISES<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Les Normes Gabonaises sont \u00e9labor\u00e9es par les comit\u00e9s techniques (CT) selon un processus qui comporte 7 \u00e9tapes :<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Stade 1: Stade proposition<\/li>\n<li>Stade 2: Stade inscription au programme annuel de normalisation<\/li>\n<li>Stade 3: Stade r\u00e9daction<\/li>\n<li>Stade 4: Stade commission<\/li>\n<li>Stade 5: Stade enqu\u00eate<\/li>\n<li>Stade 6: Stade homologation<\/li>\n<li>Stade 7: Stade \u00e9dition<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Un r\u00e9sum\u00e9 de chacun des 7 stades concern\u00e9s est donn\u00e9 ci-dessous.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-7a1803326b465f60bed8e3d4441c16ee\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 1 : Stade de proposition<\/h3>\n<p>La premi\u00e8re \u00e9tape de l\u2019\u00e9laboration d\u2019une Norme Gabonaise vient suite \u00e0 un besoin observ\u00e9 dans un secteur d\u2019activit\u00e9 donn\u00e9 o\u00f9\u00a0 elle est l\u2019expression d\u2019une saisine gouvernementale.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-42afa0ec3c7b23bfe556395566b212b4\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 2 : Inscription au programme annuel de normalisation<\/h3>\n<p>Les projets de normes propos\u00e9s sont inscrits dans le programme annuel d\u2019\u00e9laboration des normes\u00a0 (PAEN) qui est \u00e9tabli sur la base des orientations du gouvernement et les besoins en normes recens\u00e9s aupr\u00e8s des partenaires \u00e9conomiques et sociaux et aupr\u00e8s des comit\u00e9s techniques de normalisation.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-5499f232192dfa1a992ca7a6e534d733\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 3 : Stade de r\u00e9daction<\/h3>\n<p>Pour l\u2019\u00e9laboration des avants projets de normes, le secr\u00e9tariat technique du comit\u00e9 technique proc\u00e8de \u00e0 la collecte des documents de base tels que les r\u00e8glements, les normes \u00e9trang\u00e8res et internationales. Les projets de normes sont pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s conform\u00e9ment au mod\u00e8le \u00e9tabli par l\u2019AGANOR.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-c44d29c688f256e88e3fd98f8eb2a919\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 4 : Stade du Comit\u00e9 Technique<\/h3>\n<p>Le secr\u00e9tariat\u00a0 technique \u00a0concern\u00e9 arr\u00eate les dates de tenue des r\u00e9unions et pr\u00e9pare ces derni\u00e8res et convoque les membres de ladite commission en veillant \u00e0 ce que toutes les parties int\u00e9ress\u00e9es soient repr\u00e9sent\u00e9es.\u00a0Le projet de norme est examin\u00e9 autant de fois qu\u2019il est n\u00e9cessaire, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019un consensus soit atteint sur le contenu technique du document. Une fois ce consensus obtenu, il est proc\u00e9d\u00e9 \u00e0 la mise au point d\u00e9finitive du texte en vue de sa soumission en enqu\u00eate publique.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-f813b7d8cd396897a21be5891b045fe6\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 5 : Stade enqu\u00eate<\/h3>\n<p>Pour s\u2019assurer que les projets de normes adopt\u00e9s par les commissions techniques correspondent \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat g\u00e9n\u00e9ral et qu\u2019ils ne soul\u00e8vent aucune remarque allant \u00e0 l\u2019encontre du d\u00e9veloppement \u00e9conomique, une large consultation (enqu\u00eate publique de 15 \u00e0 60 jours) est organis\u00e9e par le secr\u00e9tariat technique \u00a0de la commission aupr\u00e8s des op\u00e9rateurs \u00e9conomiques via les diff\u00e9rents m\u00e9dias.\u00a0Les observations formul\u00e9es au cours de l\u2019enqu\u00eate publique sont examin\u00e9es par le comit\u00e9 technique \u00a0de normalisation concern\u00e9e qui en tient compte pour l\u2019\u00e9laboration \u00a0de la \u00a0norme Gabonaise\u00a0 d\u00e9finitive.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-aa8618123216103576a2ccbb4d59449c\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 6: Stade homologation<\/h3>\n<p>Les d\u00e9cisions d\u2019homologation des normes sont soumises au visa du Directeur de l\u2019AGANOR et transmises pour publication au Journal Officiel (JO).<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-2864aafdaaa0da49c5af72bb353087e6\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stade 7 : Stade \u00e9dition<\/h3>\n<p>Lorsque l\u2019homologation\u00a0 d\u2019une \u00a0Norme est acquise. Le texte d\u00e9finitif est envoy\u00e9 pour impression finale pour proc\u00e9der \u00e0 la publication de la Norme Gabonaise.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-a12649468eeaa03d317ecdcd0140308a\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-bbcae8159577381b32c5749c561cca31\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":12148,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12263"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=12263"}],"version-history":[{"count":24,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12263\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14036,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12263\/revisions\/14036"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12148"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=12263"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}